      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s in really wonderful shape! It\u2019s been super dependable for me, runs like a dream, and still looks great parked in the driveway. It\u2019s perfect for someone who wants a solid, well-loved vehicle without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019ve taken care of it, and I\u2019d love for it to go to a great home. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
