    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900-RPM redline. This example is tailored for the purist, featuring a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive Vanos overhaul and rod bearing replacement. The chassis is reinforced at the rear subframe mounting points and utilizes upgraded bushings for sharpened turn-in and lateral stability. While the finish shows minor road-derived patina, the powertrain exhibits excellent compression and linear power delivery, maintaining the tactile feedback and analog engagement synonymous with this BMW M-division icon.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
