    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of luxury and reliability, having been kept in excellent running order throughout its life. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though closer inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with careful highway driving. The alloy wheels are clean, wrapped in tires with plenty of tread remaining. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any rips or stains, and the original floor mats have protected the carpets perfectly. Every feature, including the panoramic sunroof, heated seats, and the intuitive infotainment system, operates exactly as it should. Mechanically, this car is robust. It has been serviced at regular intervals, with a recent oil change and brake inspection performed just last month. The engine is responsive and quiet, while the transmission provides seamless shifts. If you are looking for a dependable, high-quality vehicle that has clearly been loved by its previous owner, this is the one.",
      "price": 35800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
